{
  "texts": [
    "Labels \"Yes\" and \"To some extent\" are merged into a single positive class, resulting in a binary classification task.",
    "The same macro-F1 and accuracy metrics are then applied to the collapsed label set.",
    "For both settings, accuracy is defined as the proportion of correct predictions over all samples:",
    "where N is the number of samples, ŷi is the predicted label, and y i is the gold label for instance i.",
    "Since the test labels were not released, we computed local metrics only on the development set."
  ]
}